    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes. We discussed this, and will find a solution (not now, in a while), where the templating would be an “open-ended” API instead of just a string. Mustache is better than Hogan as a replacement; but it’s a few KB bigger, and we don’t want to switch for that now. Have you been able to change your CSP with the latest version?",
